{"type": "article", "id": 20241, "title": "五边形坐垫", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-05T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141715gJ2Mpt6BaEjYU1uD.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一组五边形的坐垫，来自挪威的设计事务所 Anderssen &amp; Voll 和丹麦的设计品牌 Muuto。它的外形类似于五角大楼，面料来自著名的织品公司 Kvadrat，顺着五条边的方向有交织的条纹，有点棕榈叶的感觉，给人一种温暖的居家气氛。有蓝色、灰色、黑色和粉红色，<a href=\"http://www.muuto.com/furniture/five-pouf\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141713YzaI6ZSCtgu0qDpM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141713RxH6YO4SwEhdWp1c.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141714E7vHesJ5TbuywgVf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.28098291\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141714ijomeCYJABSwkDT7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.27777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}